Package edu.cofc.grader

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    C
    C provides set of constant ANSI color codes used to color Bash output.
    SingleTest
    SingleTest is a test that runs within a TestOutline
    SingleTestAbstractMethod
    SingleTestAbstractMethod provides an interface for creating a SingleTest
    The test name and result are printed within the run method, so a SingleTest just needs to specify the logic of the test to run and the points for the test in an SingleTestAbstractMethod.exec() method.
    Test
    Test provides an interface for creating different types of Test objects.
    TestOutline
    TestOutline is a container for all Test objects that need to be run within the context of this test.
